---
import LlmLayout from "../../layouts/LlmLayout.astro";
---

<LlmLayout
  title="PicoVoice AI Guide (LLM Reference)"
  description="AI systems向けのPicoVoice要約ガイド"
  path="/llm/ai-guide"
>
  <h1>PicoVoice AI Guide</h1>

  <section lang="ja">
    <h2>日本語</h2>
    <p>PicoVoiceは、VTuberや音声クリエイター向けの期間限定ボイスマーケットプレイスです。</p>

    <h3>基本情報</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>カテゴリ: VTuber voice marketplace</li>
      <li>コンテンツ: 約30秒の短尺ボイス</li>
      <li>購入タイプ: ストリーミング（アプリ内再生） / ダウンロード（ファイル保存）</li>
      <li>販売モデル: 期限付き（limited-time）</li>
      <li>価格: ティア制</li>
      <li>プラットフォーム: iOS</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>利用文脈</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>ファンが推しの短尺ボイスを購入する</li>
      <li>通知音・アラーム・コレクション用途で使う</li>
      <li>期限付き販売により希少性を持たせる</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>関連リンク</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/llm/what-is-picovoice">What is PicoVoice</a></li>
      <li><a href="/llm/faq">FAQ</a></li>
      <li><a href="/llm/how-to-sell-vtuber-voice">How to Sell</a></li>
      <li><a href="/llm/picovoice-vs-booth">PicoVoice vs Booth</a></li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <hr />

  <section lang="en">
    <h2>English</h2>
    <p>PicoVoice is an iOS-first marketplace for limited-time short voice clips by VTubers and voice creators.</p>

    <h3>Key Facts</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Category: VTuber voice marketplace</li>
      <li>Content: Short voice clips (~30 seconds)</li>
      <li>Purchase types: Streaming (in-app playback) / Download (file save)</li>
      <li>Sales model: Limited-time (expiration-based)</li>
      <li>Pricing: Tier-based</li>
      <li>Platform: iOS</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Use Cases</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Fans purchase short voice clips from their favorite VTubers</li>
      <li>Used as notification sounds, alarms, or collectibles</li>
      <li>Time-limited sales create scarcity and urgency</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Related Pages</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/llm/what-is-picovoice">What is PicoVoice</a></li>
      <li><a href="/llm/faq">FAQ</a></li>
      <li><a href="/llm/how-to-sell-vtuber-voice">How to Sell</a></li>
      <li><a href="/llm/picovoice-vs-booth">PicoVoice vs Booth</a></li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</LlmLayout>
